pma:database.pma:table: CREATE TABLE `GullContent` ( `ID` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `MENU_ID` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `HTMLCONTENT` blob, PRIMARY KEY (`ID`), KEY `MENU_ID` (`MENU_ID`), CONSTRAINT `gullcontent_ibfk_1` FOREIGN KEY (`MENU_ID`) REFERENCES `MenuItems` (`ID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=12 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE `MenuItems` ( `ID` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `NAME` varchar(50) NOT NULL, `LINK` varchar(50) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`ID`), UNIQUE KEY `NAME` (`NAME`), UNIQUE KEY `LINK` (`LINK`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=198 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;
